Just to bring up a small point. A patent, just like a tradename, has to 
be defended to stay valid. If RSA posted a FAQ giving the impression that 
they will allow use of the software AND they don't defend the patent 
(i.e. through legal action) then they will lose the right to the patent 
I found this out from some people whom this happen to. Or go ask a patent 
lawyer
